OL,3,CPaul Taylor murderer Jack Crawley to
OL,4,Cserve at least 37 years behind bars
OL,6,FThe family of Paul Taylor say they are
OL,7,Fserving a life sentence as his
OL,8,Fmurderer was ordered to serve almost
OL,9,Ffour decades behind bars.
OL,11,FJack Crawley, now 20, has been handed
OL,12,Fa mandatory life term at Carlisle
OL,13,FCrown Court.
OL,15,FJurors convicted him of both the
OL,16,Fmurder of married dad-of-two Mr Taylor
OL,17,Fand the attempted murder of a second
OL,18,Fman also aged in his 50s just 79 days
OL,19,Flater.
