OL,3,CPaul Taylor murderer Jack Crawley to
OL,4,Cserve at least 37 years behind bars
OL,6,FMr Justice Goose ruled that Crawley, a
OL,7,Fformer hospital security guard and
OL,8,Fleisure centre lifeguard, must spend a
OL,9,Fminimum of 37 years in jail before
OL,10,Fbeing considered for release.
OL,12,FMr Taylor, 56, of Annan, had his head
OL,13,F"completely smashed in" by hammer-
OL,14,Fwielding Crawley after they met for a
OL,15,Flate-night sex hook-up in Carlisle
OL,16,Flast October.
OL,18,FThey earlier chatted on the dating app
OL,19,FGrindr.
