OL,3,CPaul Taylor murderer Jack Crawley to
OL,4,Cserve at least 37 years behind bars
OL,6,FJurors heard how the Army veteran and
OL,7,Ffather-of-two desperately tried to
OL,8,Fdefend himself from the fatal attack
OL,9,Fon October 18, 2023.
OL,11,FCrawley hauled Mr Taylor's body into
OL,12,Fthe boot of his own car and drove to a
OL,13,Fwildlife watcher's woodland haven near
OL,14,Fthe city where he torched and hid the
OL,15,Fcorpse. He later cleaned the car and
OL,16,Ftried to sell it for #2,000.
