OL,3,CPaul Taylor murderer Jack Crawley to
OL,4,Cserve at least 37 years behind bars
OL,6,FFor nearly seven months, Mr Taylor's
OL,7,Ftraumatised family agonised over his
OL,8,Fwhereabouts until Crawley led
OL,9,Fdetectives to the skeletal remains in
OL,10,FMay.
OL,12,FAs Crawley was sentenced for his
OL,13,Fmurder at Carlisle Crown Court, a
OL,14,Fmoving statement from Mr Taylor's
OL,15,Fheartbroken wife, Maria, told how her
OL,16,Ffamily's lives and world had been
OL,17,F"completely torn apart".
OL,19,F"To his friends and family, Paul was
OL,20,Fthere for them whenever they needed a
OL,21,Ftrue and loyal friend," she stated.
