OL,6,F"Paul would do anything for the kids,
OL,7,Ffrom lifts to Edinburgh for Dom or
OL,8,Flifts on nights out for Beth and her
OL,9,Ffriends.
OL,11,F"We had plans for growing old
OL,12,Ftogether, travelling Scotland and
OL,13,Fhopefully becoming grandparents one
OL,14,Fday. This has all been taken away by
OL,15,FJack ` not only Paul's life but our
OL,16,Fhopes and dreams."
