OL,6,FMaria said the murder would affect her
OL,7,Fforever. She continued: "For many
OL,8,Fyears Paul worked to protect his
OL,9,Fcountry, giving up time being a
OL,10,Fhusband and father.
OL,12,F"Now was the time for us to be that
OL,13,Ffamily unit and we grieve the loss of
OL,14,Fthat, of our future.
OL,16,F"I will never have the opportunity to
OL,17,Fhear from Paul regarding his lifestyle
OL,18,Fchoices and I do not judge him; only
OL,19,Fthat we have been robbed of the time
OL,20,Fto discuss and get answers for both me
OL,21,Fand the kids.
