OL,6,F"So many questions will forever be
OL,7,Funanswered."
OL,9,FMr Taylor's son Dom said: "Dad won't
OL,10,Fbe here for the rest of our lives, to
OL,11,Fbe a part of big events like weddings
OL,12,For to meet our children.
OL,14,F"We will never hear dad's side of the
OL,15,Fstory and why he felt the need to live
OL,16,Fhis life in such a way."
