OL,6,FDaughter Beth stated: "My dad being
OL,7,Ftaken away from me means that I will
OL,8,Fnever have the opportunity to walk
OL,9,Fdown the aisle with my dad at my
OL,10,Fwedding.
OL,12,F"He will never be able to meet our
OL,13,Fchildren, and I will never be able to
OL,14,Fexperience him being the grandad that
OL,15,FI knew he would've been.
OL,17,F"The impact Jack has had on our family
OL,18,Fwill impact us for the rest of our
OL,19,Flives. Dad served to defend our
OL,20,Fcountry and to have some boy rip that
OL,21,Faway from us is unforgivable."
