OL,6,FShe added: "We all love and miss him
OL,7,Fdearly. This is a life sentence for us
OL,8,Ffrom Jack's actions and should be a
OL,9,Flife sentence for him for what he has
OL,10,Fput us through. He will remain in our
OL,11,Fthoughts forever."
OL,13,FMr Taylor's younger sister, Angela
OL,14,FMalloy, said he was a fantastic
OL,15,Fhusband, father, brother, son, uncle,
OL,16,Fnephew, cousin and friend.
OL,18,FCrawley murdered him in an "unearthly
OL,19,Fand inhumane way", she stated, adding:
OL,20,F"I believe that Jack is a risk to
OL,21,Fsociety and a danger to others."
